---
import "./FaqBlock.scss";
---

<section class="FaqBlock block" id="faq">
	<div class="_container">
		<h2 class="FaqBlock__title anim_scroll" data-anim-index="0">
			FAQ
		</h2>
		<div class="FaqBlock__cards anim_scroll" data-anim-index="1">
			<button class="FaqBlock__card">
				<div class="FaqBlock__card-front">
					<h3 class="FaqBlock__card-question">
						How does NoRekt prevent liquidations?
					</h3>
				</div>
				<div class="FaqBlock__card-back">
					<div class="FaqBlock__card-answer">
						<p>
							NoRekt hedges your collateral using other instruments. If your collateral drops in value, your hedge gains the same amount â€” your account stays healthy.
						</p>
						<p>
							Example: ETH drops 30%, your hedge gains 30%. Net effect: $0 loss. No liquidation.
						</p>
						<p>
							Protection activates via hedge contracts or auto-hedge positions
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</button>
			<button class="FaqBlock__card">
				<div class="FaqBlock__card-front">
					<h3 class="FaqBlock__card-question">
						What assets can I use as collateral?
					</h3>
				</div>
				<div class="FaqBlock__card-back">
					<div class="FaqBlock__card-answer">
						Currently, we support ETH as collateral. Additional assets will be supported in future protocol updates
					</div>
				</div>
			</button>
			<button class="FaqBlock__card">
				<div class="FaqBlock__card-front">
					<h3 class="FaqBlock__card-question">
						How is the fee calculated?
					</h3>
				</div>
				<div class="FaqBlock__card-back">
					<div class="FaqBlock__card-answer">
						Interest rate is variable, like other lending protocols. It depends on: utilization rate and asset type
					</div>
				</div>
			</button>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>